data.description: This 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath home is a true diamond!!!!  Located in a popular community, this Beautiful Home features a Family room, Living room, plus an air conditioned Florida room with glass windows and a split Bedroom and Open Floor plan.  The beautifully updated Kitchen has tons of storage, pantry, deep sink, recessed lighting, separate coffee bar, and the Refrigerator, Microwave and Disposal are all new in 2023.  The roof was installed in 2021, a new hot water heater installed in 2022 and the utility room was insulated in 2022.  The home has double paned windows with efficient hurricane shutters and newer vinyl siding.  The large Master suite has a great walk in closet and an updated bath with a step in tile shower.  The guest Bath has also been updated with beautiful tile in the shower.  The home has been semi-modified to accommodate a wheelchair.  Some of the furnishings are available in a separate sale.
